00:04:42.430 --> 00:04:44.680
MALE SPEAKER: So let's
start with some definitions.

00:04:44.680 --> 00:04:45.020
MICHAEL HORN: OK.

00:04:45.020 --> 00:04:45.960
MALE SPEAKER: So you
have an audience here,

00:04:45.960 --> 00:04:47.774
some that get what
we're talking about,

00:04:47.774 --> 00:04:49.690
some that don't know
