What do you see happening
in that space, what could

00:22:29.680 --> 00:22:31.320
we all do better in that space?

00:22:31.320 --> 00:22:32.430
MICHAEL HORN: I'm worried.

00:22:32.430 --> 00:22:39.100
I think if we hit 50% 2019 and
we've replicated the factory

00:22:39.100 --> 00:22:40.370
model online.

00:22:42.890 --> 00:22:43.690
What's today?

00:22:43.690 --> 00:22:45.300
May 7.

00:22:45.300 --> 00:22:47.910
You were born in the
year the lamb, therefore

00:22:47.910 --> 00:22:50.539
we're all doing
double-digit addition,

00:22:50.539 --> 00:22:51.580
like we've really failed.

00:22:51.580 --> 00:22:53.400
And I think there's
a big risk of that,

00:22:53.400 --> 00:22:55.560
so I think a couple
things we have to do.

00:22:55.560 --> 00:22:59.740
