devices, cell phones or maybe

00:26:01.240 --> 00:26:02.480
tablets.

00:26:02.480 --> 00:26:07.172
How do you do content delivery
on a small device effectively?

00:26:07.172 --> 00:26:09.130
MICHAEL HORN: And this
