00:26:12.710 --> 00:26:15.810
of what we think
good content has

00:26:15.810 --> 00:26:18.440
to be is I think we have to
take a very different mindset

00:26:18.440 --> 00:26:21.970
and understand how they're
getting content today,

00:26:21.970 --> 00:26:25.720
or not getting content, and then
what is a good enough state,

00:26:25.720 --> 00:26:28.110
and then what sets it
on a trajectory that

00:26:28.110 --> 00:26:29.540
starts to improve.

00:26:29.540 --> 00:26:31.272
And I think that's
tough sometimes

00:26:31.272 --> 00:26:33.355
when we're talking about
improving social sectors,

00:26:33.355 --> 00:26:36.019
as like something that's
not perfect but good enough,

00:26:36.019 --> 00:26:38.310
but that's the coin in the
realm with disruption, which

00:26:38.310 --> 00:26:40.780
is like when the Google
search engine started

00:26:40.780 --> 00:26:43.470
it doesn't do all that it did
now, but it was good enough.

00:26:43.470 --> 00:26:45.030
It was good enough
to get it started

00:26:45.030 --> 00:26:50.200
and change the way we view
information and content,

00:26:50.200 --> 00:26:52.834
and so I think getting a
good enough perspective is

00:26:52.834 --> 00:26:53.500
the first thing.

00:26:53.500 --> 00:26:55.990
The second thing I
think-- this is probably

00:26:55.990 --> 00:26:58.930
somewhat controversial, but
I think in Silicon Valley

00:26:58.930 --> 00:27:02.120
