for you to create a constantly

00:29:00.465 --> 00:29:04.910
a iterating,
improving innovation,

00:29:04.910 --> 00:29:07.350
and I think the real messages
is like, you know what,

00:29:07.350 --> 00:29:09.800
even if you nailed it
for today circumstance,

00:29:09.800 --> 00:29:12.610
in 10 years from now societies
going to change some more

00:29:12.610 --> 00:29:15.720
and we need to keep evolving
and innovating with that.

00:29:15.720 --> 00:29:20.360
So how do you do
that, and I think

00:29:20.360 --> 00:29:22.050
we need to stop
thinking of school

00:29:22.050 --> 00:29:24.415
as like a finished product
that OK, that's it,

00:29:24.415 --> 00:29:25.630
let's all do that.

00:29:25.630 --> 00:29:26.549
MALE SPEAKER: Exactly.

00:29:26.549 --> 00:29:27.090
AUDIENCE: Hi.

00:29:27.090 --> 00:29:29.690
So you mentioned that we
need a platform to emerge

00:29:29.690 --> 00:29:31.510
to kind of pull some
of the student data

00:29:31.510 --> 00:29:34.056
