project-based learning.

00:41:17.820 --> 00:41:20.236
So a lot of it has to do with
the definitions that we use.

00:41:20.236 --> 00:41:21.869
MICHAEL HORN: I agree with that.

00:41:21.869 --> 00:41:22.660
MALE SPEAKER: Yeah?

