00:49:20.010 --> 00:49:20.780
back there.

00:49:20.780 --> 00:49:24.990
You can get it on Amazon, Google
Play, and other places as well.

00:49:24.990 --> 00:49:27.510
So last question for
you before we wrap up.

00:49:27.510 --> 00:49:29.964
What can we do to help?

00:49:29.964 --> 00:49:32.380
MICHAEL HORN: So I think Google
